# 🏏 IPL Match Predictor

A web-based application that predicts IPL match outcomes based on match conditions like runs, overs, and wickets.

## 🚀 Live Demo
👉 https://himadrigoswami2606-coder.github.io/IPL_Predictor/

---

## 📊 Features
- Predict match outcome based on match inputs
- Interactive user interface
- Real-time prediction logic
- Fast and responsive design

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- GitHub Pages (Deployment)

---

## 🧠 How It Works
The application takes match inputs such as:
- Runs scored
- Overs completed
- Wickets lost

Based on these inputs, it applies logical conditions to estimate the probability of winning.

